    "body" : "<p>2 options:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Make a value class that holds the 2 things you need.</li>\n<li>Or, for simple\ncases, just use a Pair class which comes with plenty of libraries,\nincluding the famous Apache Commons library. i.e. <code>Pair&lt;UUID, Event&gt; pair = Pair.of(id, event)</code></li>\n</ol>\n"
