  "title" : "Store &quot;tuples&quot; of values in ArrayList in Java",
  "body" : "<p>I'm trying to store pairs of names and addresses in a collection. Is there a way these values can be grouped together in a tuple? If so, which collection should I use to fulfill this? Whatever collection I use, it should be able to add a tuple with these values, remove the tuple, and list the tuples in the collection.</p>\n"
